headline: Morgan Stanley Lowers PT on Synopsys (SNPS), Maintains an Overweight Rating
summary: Synopsys, Inc. (NASDAQ:SNPS) is one of the Best NASDAQ Stocks to Buy with Huge Upside Potential.
